OL,3,CHomes destroyed by early hours fire
OL,5,FA number of houses have been gutted
OL,6,Ffollowing a fire in Sheffield.
OL,8,FFirefighters were called to Foxhill
OL,9,FRoad in the Grenoside area at about
OL,10,F4am on Thursday after a blaze
OL,11,Faffecting five terraced properties.
OL,13,FPictures from the scene showed two of
OL,14,Fthe houses virtually destroyed, but it
OL,15,Fis not known if anyone was injured.
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Fire Service said the
OL,18,Fcause of the fire was being
OL,19,Finvestigated.
