OL,3,CHomes destroyed by early hours fire
OL,5,FFoxhill Road remained closed on
OL,6,FThursday morning.
OL,8,FA fire service spokesperson said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts are with all the residents
OL,10,Faffected by this very serious fire."
OL,12,FThe Foxhill Forum community offered
OL,13,Fhelp and drinks to residents who were
OL,14,Ftold to leave their homes.
